column2: Hepatocyte Subclustering of Single-cell Analysis SC22147

This is a subclustering analysis of single-cell analysis SC22147. For this subclustering analysis cells from the B-cell cluster (C5), Hepatocyte cluster (C8) and Neutropil cluster (C19) in experiment SC22147 were selected. In this selection, sample SubcutNoLiverMetM2R2 featured only 5 cells and was excluded from this subclustering analysis.
